## ğŸ“˜ Project Description

This repository includes a detailed study of **major network security threats** that affect computer networks today.

The report explains how different cyberattacks are carried out, the damage they can cause, and the security measures used to protect networks from such threats.

The main purpose of this project is to improve understanding of network security concepts as part of academic coursework and practical learning.

